data.name: Guardragon Reincarnation
data.desc: Fusion Summon 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, by banishing Fusion Materials listed on it, that are all Link Monsters, from your field or GY. You can only activate 1 "Guardragon Reincarnation" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
